title: My Pixel 5 is not working in 5G mode in my enabled plan with Zain provider in Kuwait pls help.
content:
I called my provider and my 5G plan is enabled. But it doesnt work with my Pixel 5 although it was working fine with my prevoious samsung phone. My provider advised me to contact google for help in unlocking the 5G in Kuwaits network. Please help. 
Thank you.
